related_questions.question: How do you measure SEO effectiveness?
related_questions.snippet: Organic click-through rate is a good KPI to measure the quality of your website. If web searches like what they see, they'll dig deeper into your site. A CTR is a straightforward metric: It's the number of times a search result gets clicked, divided by how many views (or impressions) the search result has received.
